              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Reaction residues were identified in the S800",
                "spectrometer using the energy loss and the time-of-",
                "flight (TOF) information of the focal plane detectors."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Deuterons were detected in the",
                "High-Resolution Array (HiRA) in coincidence with the",
                "recoil residues detected in the S800 focal plane.An",
                "array of 16 HiRA telescopes was placed at 35 cm from",
                "the target where they subtended laboratory polar angles",
                "between 6deg and 45deg. Each telescope contained",
                "65 mu-m thick dE and 1500 mu-m thick E silicon strip",
                "detectors, backed by 3.9 cm thick CsI(Tl) crystals."
              ]
            }
          ],
